      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an extraordinary example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is offered in pristine, showroom condition, having been preserved with an uncompromising commitment to maintenance and care. The exterior finish retains its original luster, while the interior remains in impeccable state, free from any signs of wear. For the collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a truly investment-grade specimen that performs as flawlessly as it looks.",
      "price": 48900.0,
